'''首都電台'''（{{lang-en|Capital FM}}）是[[英國|英國]]12家獨立的[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]的電臺網，播放本地和網絡節目。其中9家電台由[[環球_(英國公司)|環球]]擁有，其他3家電台則根據單獨的特許協議擁有。<ref>[http://www.maclaurinmedia.com/blog/uk_tunes_into_capital_fm/ UK Tunes into Capital FM] MacLaurin Media, 4 January 2011 {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320140115/http://www.maclaurinmedia.com/blog/uk_tunes_into_capital_fm/ |date=20 March 2012 }}</ref>

截至2018年6月，各台每週合計服務740萬聽眾，核心聽眾鎖定在15-34歲年齡段，57%的聽衆在此年齡段。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.global.com/radio/capital-fm/audience/#stats |title=The Audience {{!}} Global |access-date=4 June 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718234533/http://www.global.com/radio/capital-fm/audience/#stats |archive-date=2018-07-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

首都電臺的[[歌單|歌單]]中歌曲很少<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.capitalfm.com/radio/playlist/|title=Capital FM|work=Capital|access-date=2018-08-28|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828204736/https://www.capitalfm.com/radio/playlist/|archive-date=28 August 2018|}}</ref>，每週只換幾首歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://radioiloveit.com/radio-music-research-music-scheduling-software/music-scheduling-music-directors-capital-fm-and-radio-hamburg/|title=Music Scheduling @ Capital FM & Radio Hamburg|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=Radioiloveit|accessdate=28 April 2013|quote=Capital FM is pure CHR and therefore hardly plays anything older than 2 years. The majority of songs is from the last 12 months, with a major focus on current hits.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608073902/http://www.radioiloveit.com/radio-music-research-music-scheduling-software/music-scheduling-music-directors-capital-fm-and-radio-hamburg/|archive-date=8 June 2013|}}</ref>與[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]不同，首都電臺不播放[[搖滾樂|搖滾樂]]、經典流行音樂或[[另類音樂|另類音樂]]。
